women next Monday,

00:46:15.450 --> 00:46:18.880
that is going to make
a statement, which

00:46:18.880 --> 00:46:20.909
no one can really ignore.

00:46:20.909 --> 00:46:22.950
And when you make a
statement, which no one can--

00:46:22.950 --> 00:46:25.030
so how many of you
are going to volunteer

00:46:25.030 --> 00:46:27.650
to come as women on Monday?

00:46:27.650 --> 00:46:30.750
You all put your hand
up you supported it.

00:46:30.750 --> 00:46:33.529
So do it.

00:46:33.529 --> 00:46:35.320
I don't mean the girls
to put your hand up.

00:46:35.320 --> 00:46:35.819
Yes.

00:46:39.520 --> 00:46:41.650
So do something like that.

00:46:41.650 --> 00:46:43.850
And you'll get some great
